{"pageProps":{"source":"<div class=\"space-y-4 whitespace-normal *:first:mt-0 *:last:mb-0\"><p>Pour installer <a class=\"\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://docker.com/\">docker</a> sur un serveur Linux (Ubuntu ou Debian), il suffit d&#x27;exécuter cette commande :</p><div class=\"relative group\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"invisible group-hover:visible absolute top-0 right-0 rounded-md text-xs bg-gray-300 m-3 p-1.5 cursor-pointer leading-none\">Copier</button><pre><code class=\"language-bash\">apt update &amp;&amp; apt install -yq docker.io\n</code></pre></div><p>Si vous êtes sur Arch Linux :</p><div class=\"relative group\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"invisible group-hover:visible absolute top-0 right-0 rounded-md text-xs bg-gray-300 m-3 p-1.5 cursor-pointer leading-none\">Copier</button><pre><code class=\"language-bash\">sudo pacman -S docker\n</code></pre></div><p>Pour le configurer :</p><div class=\"relative group\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"invisible group-hover:visible absolute top-0 right-0 rounded-md text-xs bg-gray-300 m-3 p-1.5 cursor-pointer leading-none\">Copier</button><pre><code class=\"language-bash\">sudo systemctl enable --now docker\ngpasswd -a &lt;user&gt; docker\nnewgrp docker\n</code></pre></div><p>Il existe aussi une <a class=\"\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://docs.docker.com/docker-for-windows/install/\">installation pour Windows</a> et une <a class=\"\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://docs.docker.com/docker-for-mac/install/\">installation pour Mac</a>.</p></div>","isIndex":false,"file":"Installer Docker.md","fileName":"Installer Docker","title":"Installer Docker","comments":true,"permalink":"installer-docker","datePublished":"2021-05-17T17:32","dateUpdated":"2021-05-17T17:32","publish":true,"note":"49"},"__N_SSG":true}